<section class="community-food">
  <img class="section-badge" src="{{ "lp-community-section-badge-food.png" | file_url }}" alt="community food">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Looking For Tasty & Healthy Food Ideas?</h2>
    <p>Everything is more enjoyable with a full belly. But, what to make? Will everyone like it? How can you get creative and avoid food boredom? It’s challenging to eat healthy.
