    If you are looking for some food inspiration, here are some of our favorite posts from other members! They're healthy, and they're NOT boring!</p>
    <div class="posts swiper">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">
      <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-food-post-1.png" | file_url }}" alt="community food post">
      <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-food-post-2.png" | file_url }}" alt="community food post">
